HEADWORD: Salting
<hw>Salt"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
of sprinkling, impregnating, or furnishing, with salt.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A salt marsh.</def>⟦br⟧
